item.title: Tracking origin of bugs with git bisect
item.description: Disect the rocket, image by ProudloveNathan Proudlove I’ve been involved with a iOS project this past week. I’m adding functionalities to the CommonSense iOS library. One of the most annoying thing is that it took about 2 minute to load the project. This is only happened in the unstable branch. The master branch seems to be working fine. So I knew that somewhere there is a commit when this starts happening.
